README
===============
Ex 1:
I defined a custom reader in class LeipzigCorpusReader, of module scripts/leipzigreader.
The exact file I used for the corpus can be downloaded directly from,
http://corpora2.informatik.uni-leipzig.de/downloads/eng-za_web_2013_100K-text.tar.gz

The size is about 11MB.

